snippet.title: Angry Birds: FPS - Magic Leap Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available on the Magic Leap One Creator Edition, Angry Birds: First Person Slingshot provides animated characters and objects overlaid onto their actual environment, bringing Angry Birds to life like never before – right in your home! #AngryBirdsFPS

For more information on Resolution Games or the game visit at www.resolutiongames.com, follow us on Twitter (https://twitter.com/resolutiongame) or like us on Facebook (https://www.facebook.com/resolutiongamesdotcom).
